Here's what you need to know to clear as Shaco:

* Level 1: Run IMMEDIATELY to  <ScMonsterCampInline camp="raptors" /> and place a box down ASAP at 0:25, then another at 0:40. You will start at <ScMonsterCampInline camp="red" />
* As you do <ScMonsterCampInline camp="red" />, the boxes will get the Big Raptor down to around 600 HP, and it will walk towards you. <ScSummonerInline summonerIdentifier="Smite" /> it to get level 2.&#x20;
* Then throughout your clears, you can leave camps at 20-30% \~ HP left with a Box to finish them off.&#x20;
* This is why we're putting 2 points in <ScAbilityInline_v2 spellKey="W" />, so we can speed up our clear leaving camps early with boxes.&#x20;

You ABSOLUTELY need to Backstab someone every time you <ScAbilityInline_v2 spellKey="Q" />.

* Your <ScAbilityInline_v2 spellKey="Q" /> guarantees a crit with a 1.6x multiplier. This also buffs your backstab damage for a huge amount of burst on your first auto.
* If using <ScAbilityInline_v2 spellKey="Q" /> over walls to move around the map, you don't need the stealth. Press B immediately to come out of stealth, letting your <ScAbilityInline_v2 spellKey="Q" /> come off CD faster.&#x20;
